        <item>
            <title>Instagram 推出 DM 新功能，移动位置共享 + 300 款贴图更新 + 设定好友暱称</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/26/instagram-dm/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=instagram-dm</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/26/instagram-dm/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 10:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instagram]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277275</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Instagram 宣布针对其讯息功能进行多项更新，重点包括新增移动位置共享、暱称设置以及全新贴图等功能，超过 300 个新贴图任用户选择。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277277 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-8-581x580.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-8-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-8.jpg 902w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-8-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 581px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Instagram 新增移动位置共享功能，让用户可与好友共享即时位置长达 1 小时（图片来源：<a href="https://about.instagram.com/blog/announcements/new-instagram-dm-features-update">Instagram</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Instagram 新增移动位置共享功能，让用户可与好友共享即时位置长达 1 小时。功能适合在现实生活中与朋友会面时使用，用户还可选择将地点标注在地图上，以便安排聚会或指引方向。 位置共享功能只限於单一好友对话及群组聊天讯息中使用，所有共享位置将在 1 小时后自动失效，并预设为关闭状态。Instagram 表示，位置资讯只限对话内成员查看，无法转发至其他对话。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277279 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-10-578x580.jpg" alt="" width="578" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-10-578x580.jpg 578w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-10.jpg 897w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-10-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 578px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用户可为自己或好友设定暱称（图片来源：<a href="https://about.instagram.com/blog/announcements/new-instagram-dm-features-update">Instagram</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Instagram 亦为讯息加入暱称设置功能，用户可为自己或好友设定暱称，方便识别较长用户名称。用户只需点击对话名称，再选择暱称功能，即可进行设置，让对话介面更加清晰易用。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277280 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-11-576x580.jpg" alt="" width="576" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-11-576x580.jpg 576w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-11.jpg 894w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241125at-11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 576px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内有 300 个新贴图供用户选择使用（图片来源：<a href="https://about.instagram.com/blog/announcements/new-instagram-dm-features-update">Instagram</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">是次更新推出了 17 款全新贴图，内有 300 个新贴图供用户选择使用，并新增贴图收藏功能，用户可将喜爱贴图加入收藏，方便随时存取。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/11/25/instagram-dm-live-location-sharing/">MacRumors</a>、<a href="https://about.instagram.com/blog/announcements/new-instagram-dm-features-update">Instagram</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/26/instagram-dm/software/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>外卖员发文申诉 Keeta 忽视员工安全   「车祸后平台无跟进 + 保险公司已读不回」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/26/keeta-3/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=keeta-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/26/keeta-3/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 09:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[饮食]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[keeta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Threads]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277315</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">有 Threads 用户发文控诉外卖平台 Keeta 处理外卖员工交通意外的方式。用户分享称，他在本月初送外卖时遭遇车祸，所幸只受轻伤，但整个过程中，平台和保险公司并未提供任何实质协助。他在贴文中表示：「Keeta 无人会跟进，保险公司亦都系已读不回」，更质疑为了微薄的准时奖是否值得冒如此大的风险。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277321 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_.jpg 832w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277332 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-8-694x513.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="513" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-8-694x513.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-8.jpg 1218w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-12-689x580.jpg" alt="" width="689" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-12-689x580.jpg 689w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-12.jpg 1069w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 689px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-11-310x580.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-11-310x580.jpg 310w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241126at-11.jpg 481w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 310px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Keeta 外卖员工遭遇车祸，平台和保险公司并未提供任何实质协助（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">有网民建议员工在遇到交通意外时应积极采取行动：「俾车撞一定要报警，再去医院验伤，有病假纸申请咗车手奖先，再自己揾师爷去 claim 对方保险公司。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1.jpg 1268w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民建议员工在遇到交通意外时应积极采取行动（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">更有网民直接批评 Keeta 的商业模式剥削外卖员工，指出：「Keeta 系好多优惠畀消费者，但系羊毛出自羊身上，Keeta 唔系自己赚少啲，而系剥削咗车手嘅人身安全，亦都系置餐饮业员工安全于不顾。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277324 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_.png 1262w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更有网民直接批评 Keeta 的商业模式剥削外卖员工（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">另一位网民强调，平台将外卖员工定位为自雇人士，令其在受伤时无法享有雇员的工伤赔偿保障：「Deliveroo 果边已经有法院判案话车手唔系雇员，除咗意外保之外，无得 claim 工伤。」更有留言质疑 Keeta 在选择保险公司时以价格为主要考量，导致外卖员工的保障不足：「Keeta 拣嘅公司一定系最平最渣，悭得就悭。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277325 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1-694x165.png" alt="" width="694" height="165" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1-694x165.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-1.png 1274w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网民强调，平台将外卖员工定位为自雇人士，令其在受伤时无法享有雇员的工伤赔偿保障（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1277326 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-2-694x117.png" alt="" width="694" height="117" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-2-694x117.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241126_-2.png 1274w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更有留言质疑 Keeta 在选择保险公司时以价格为主要考量，导致外卖员工的保障不足（图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@billy_bloooom/post/DCyKmkRzpJW?xmt=AQGzkr3wXuu7ZXjhpw07kgp8MV9pX-BaQM5AAFzssxDvqQ">Threads</a>、<a href="https://www.foodtalks.cn/news/45954">foodtalks</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
